record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 3192
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 3192 -- (House of Representatives - June 20, 2008)

[Page: H5774]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that my name be removed as a cosponsor of H.R. 3192.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from California?
